title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - City Update 3 - now available
description:
In this video we will have a quick look what has been included in City Update 3. The thing which surprised me is that this CU is coming really soon after City Update 2 which has been recently released. However if you review the release notes and after that look at the download size you understand why this one could be release pretty quick.
